<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="un6023bg"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="un6" href="#un6023">UN6: </a>  <a href="../../FF/unbs/un6all.htm#un6023bg"> (NLI.4) 23(bg)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> debtors&apos; prison,</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">On quitting the castle, we pass the <mark>Debtors&apos; Prison</mark>, a building deserving little notice. Constructed originally for military purposes, it has long been converted to its present use; the interior has been of late rendered more commodious, but since the introduction of the bankrupt laws and insolvent act, the number of inmates has diminished as the accommodation has increased. <small> An Old Inhabitant, <a name="TTHG1" href="/udra/udex.htm#TTHG1"><cite title="source">The traveller's handbook for Gibraltar</cite></a> (1844), 21</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c07249i" href="../../../F/FF/fnbs/c07all.htm#c07249i">VI.C.07:249(i)</a> </dd> </dd></dl>
